articles.description: Members of the Louisville men's basketball team that won the 2013 national title have criticized the NCAA for its ruling Tuesday to have the championship vacated. "We won those games," Luke Hancock said. "It's not like that never happened."

images.name: Postel: NCAA is 'simply wrong' on denying Louisville appeal
